- Kenai.
- Sitka, no, you gotta get out of here.

00:12:04.933 --> 00:12:06.810
- What?
- The bear. Behind you.

00:12:10.230 --> 00:12:12.483
Hey, bear, come on. Over here.

00:12:12.857 --> 00:12:14.859
Come on, bear, come this way.

00:12:28.623 --> 00:12:29.795
Denahi!

