Sitka. Sitka!

00:13:32.020 --> 00:13:33.192
Sitka.

00:13:45.450 --> 00:13:47.373
Come on!

00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:53.174
- Sitka!
- Sitka!

00:13:55.168 --> 00:13:57.295
Sitka. Sitka!

