You know, I was thinking now
might be a good time for me to drive.

00:46:31.872 --> 00:46:34.421
Just relax and enjoy the ride.

00:46:34.500 --> 00:46:36.218
Yeah. Okay.

00:46:37.169 --> 00:46:38.546
Whee.

