Kenai, where are you?

00:52:27.061 --> 00:52:29.655
Left. Left. No, the other left.

00:52:43.160 --> 00:52:44.252
Kenai!

00:52:49.416 --> 00:52:51.168
Whoa! Whoa!

00:53:06.767 --> 00:53:08.440
No!

